I should be there.

09:12.040 --> 09:16.076
If things turn ugly, you'll need
a cool heid on square shoulders.

09:18.068 --> 09:20.088
A Liam Neeson type.

09:20.088 --> 09:22.036
Someone with a...

09:22.036 --> 09:24.060
AS LIAM NEESON:..certain set
of skills.

09:26.000 --> 09:27.084
