10:40.008 --> 10:42.076
Insufficient funds?

10:45.016 --> 10:47.076
Right...

10:47.076 --> 10:49.016
It's ringing.

10:49.016 --> 10:51.032
RINGING

10:51.032 --> 10:53.036
Oh! Look at that.

10:53.036 --> 10:55.020
Oh, hello, boys.

10:55.020 --> 10:56.048
Hello, Shug.

