12:24.036 --> 12:26.072
Are you sharing a room?

12:28.052 --> 12:29.080
Yes.

12:29.080 --> 12:31.096
ALL LAUGH KNOWINGLY

12:34.000 --> 12:35.024
Sorry, Shug.

12:38.020 --> 12:39.056
That's him away.

12:41.000 --> 12:43.052
Well, did you get it?What?

12:43.052 --> 12:45.080
Cos Australia's upside down!

12:51.080 --> 12:53.024
Isa, what are you doing?

12:53.024 --> 12:55.024
Just a wee bit of tidying.

12:55.024 --> 12:58.004
You're making me feel like Julia
Roberts in Sleeping With The Enemy.

12:58.004 --> 12:59.072
What is with the OCD pish?

12:59.072 --> 13:01.060
Your shift ended ten minutes ago.

13:01.060 --> 13:04.044
I've been building up
to ask you something.

13:04.044 --> 13:06.032
I need an advance.

13:06.032 --> 13:08.044
Naw. Have a nice evening.

13:08.044 --> 13:10.068
Oh, right.

13:10.068 --> 13:11.088
Hold on, Isa.

13:11.088 --> 13:14.028
